{"tid":1531919,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"搞Fake News, 不如整返個Fact Check認證啦","createTime":"2019-09-02T11:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:54.000Z","uid":266401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef3d6189904865fa5b25b803b10b361bc649132e","tid":1531919,"uid":266401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"我知道現在已經有負責Fact Check的Telegram Group<br />\n所以我想講的重點係「認證」<br />\n<br />\n以下是我初步的構想，希望引起大家的討論：<br />\n1) 建立一個大眾可以閱覽的Google Excel<br />\n<br />\n2) 為訊息加添一個識別ID並進行Fact Check<br />\n<br />\n3) 把Fact Check的結果連同識別ID、參考資料來源、備註等放在Google Excel內<br />\n<br />\n4) 在平台上分享訊息的時候如果想使用[Fact Checked], 請附上該新聞的識別ID<br />\n<br />\np.s. 講究一點，可以設計一個認證icon再加上識別ID<br />\n例如：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XF4AyyU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXF4AyyU.png&h=6a6aca31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a26754ea30a8db62d5f6b5823208a3525dfa32f","tid":1531919,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:14:06.000Z","msg":"QR code有無得諗?"},{"pid":"07eefeda294a54ae1dfa646dc6be976542c710b3","tid":1531919,"uid":266401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a26754ea30a8db62d5f6b5823208a3525dfa32f","tid":1531919,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:14:06.000Z","msg":"QR code有無得諗?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:21:54.000Z","msg":"可以啊！<br />\n果然大家一起討論會有更完善的念頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}